{"tid":2285793,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★阿里巴巴 面臨美國集體訴訟","createTime":"2020-11-14T11:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T13:41:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"68ece1f639482c64cf4d94d750fa9f997471d8ed","tid":2285793,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T11:58:45.000Z","msg":"螞蟻集團上市「撻Q」餘波未了！外媒報道，有美國投資者周五(13日)入稟美國聯邦法院，擬向阿里巴巴(09988)及其首席執行官張勇和首席財務官武衞提出集體訴訟，指控他們在螞蟻集團上市一事上作出失實或誤導的聲明。<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴持有33%螞蟻集團股權。訴訟文件指出，螞蟻集團上市「滑鐵盧」導致阿里巴巴股價「跌8%至約285美元。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201114/bkn-20201114163236985-1114_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20201114%2Fbkn-20201114163236985-1114_00842_001.html&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy8v4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=f3e09e3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201114/bkn-20201114163236985-1114_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ac39a04bb8e2286a6ffbc49d890a66d888a7eb92","tid":2285793,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T11:59:01.000Z","msg":"drop to $0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5088927ed3538907a27da65fd7100f0a9a6710","tid":2285793,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T11:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63a269139abbb98457e4f3972bb5961